('gallin_update','Gallin Warehouse Update','Gallin','Runs the Gallin warehouse update chain.','Daily at 21:00','Server local time',NULL,'Gallin slotting and operational data may become stale.','https://github.com/benthud82/gallin_logic','Production wrapper schedules update_gallin_tables.bat at 21:00. Batch PHP and heatmap_recommender hops were traced from the production bat.',1,1,'2026-07-17 00:00:00',0,0),
