('offsys_slot_update_CAN','Canada Nightly Slotting Pipeline','Canada Slotting','Runs the Canada warehouse data and slotting update chain.','Daily at 03:12','Server local time',NULL,'Canada slotting and operational reporting may become stale.','https://github.com/benthud82/heatmap_logic','Production chain traced through update_CAN.bat into Canada PHP table-update scripts.',1,1,'2026-07-17 00:00:00',0,0),
('nahsi_shorts_item','NAHSI Item Shorts Refresh','NAHSI Shorts','Refreshes item shorts and related operational tables on a five-minute weekday cadence.','Every 5 minutes Mon-Fri 04:00-23:55','US/Eastern',NULL,'Live shorts and expeditor surfaces may show stale item shortages.','https://github.com/benthud82/heatmap_logic','Production wrapper schedules five active batches; PHP hops traced from those bats. Obsolete CAN shorts bat call is not cataloged.',1,1,'2026-07-17 00:00:00',0,0),
